summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to and amending Page 24-219 of the Seattle Municipal Code (Plat 219W), page 3 of the official Zoning map of the City of Seattle, Ordinance 86300), to rezone certain property located on the east side of Greenwood Avenue North approximately 516 feet south of North 137th St. from Duplex Residence Medium Density (RD 7200) Zone to Multiple Residence Low Density (RM 800) Zone and accepting a Property Use and Development Agreement in connection therewith (Petition of Thomas B. Harader; CF No. 290515.
